Noun of action from English '''[[beautify]]''', ''make beautiful'', from '''[[beauty]]''', from French '''[[beaute]]''', from Latin '''[[bellitas]]''', ''beauty'' or ''beautifulness'', noun of state from '''[[bellus]]''', ''beautiful'', + noun of state suffix '''[[-tas]]'''.

